1930;;Safety in Numbers;;American;;Victor Schertzinger;;Carole Lombard, Charles Rogers, Kathryn Crawford;;musical, comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Safety_in_Numbers_(1930_film);;William Reynolds is set to inherit $350 million on his next birthday, but his uncle says he must learn the ways of the world beforehand. His uncle hires three follies girls to guide William around New York.[1]